    "patch_code": "private String getRemainingJSDocLine() throws ParseException {\n  String result = stream.getRemainingJSDocLine();\n  if(result == null || !result.contains(\".\")){\n      throw new ParseException(\"\\nParsing error\", -1);\n  }\n  return result;\n}",
